N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 204.16 - Certification course facilities

State Regulations

Each course shall be presented in such premises or such
facilities, whether physical or virtual, as shall be necessary to properly
present the course. Such premises or facilities shall be preapproved by the
division. Notes
